<div class="quote"><blockquote><font size="2"><font color="#999999">深山悠悠 发表于 2015-2-26 11:08</font> <a href="http://bbs.rednet.cn/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=82041168&amp;ptid=43939444" target="_blank"><img id="aimg_hj0Mt" onclick="zoom(this, this.src, 0, 0, 1)" class="zoom" file="static/image/common/back.gif" onmouseover="img_onmouseoverfunc(this)" lazyloadthumb="1" border="0" alt="" /></a></font><br />
